origin_description: He was born Kal-El on the planet Krypton, before being rocketed to Earth as an infant by his scientist father Jor-El, moments before Krypton's destruction...
superpowers: solar energy absorption and healing factor
catch_phrase: Look, up in the sky, it's a bird, it's a plane, it's Superman!

origin_description: After witnessing the murder of his parents Dr. Thomas Wayne and Martha Wayne as a child, Bruce Wayne swore vengeance against criminals, an oath tempered by a sense of justice...

Diana, princess of the Amazons, trained to be an unconquerable warrior. Raised on a sheltered island paradise, when a pilot crashes on their shores and tells of a massive conflict raging in the outside world, Diana leaves her home, convinced she can stop the threat.
catch_phrase: I will fight for those who cannot fight for themselves.

origin_description: Peter Parker, a high school student, gained the abilities of a spider after being bitten by a radioactive spider. With his newfound powers, he fights crime as the friendly neighborhood Spider-Man.
catch_phrase: With great power comes great responsibility.

origin_description: Steve Rogers, a frail young man, volunteered for a military experiment that transformed him into the super-soldier known as Captain America. He fights for justice and embodies the ideals of courage, loyalty, and patriotism.
catch_phrase: I can do this all day.

origin_description: Natasha Romanoff, also known as Black Widow, is a highly skilled spy and assassin. She is a former agent of S.H.I.E.L.D. and a member of the Avengers. With her expertise in combat and espionage, she fights against threats to global security.
catch_phrase: I'm always picking up after you boys.

origin_description: Thor Odinson, the god of thunder, wields the enchanted hammer Mjolnir. As a member of the Asgardian race, he protects Earth from various threats and is a founding member of the Avengers.
catch_phrase: I am Thor, son of Odin!

origin_description: Bruce Banner, a scientist, gained the ability to transform into the Hulk after being exposed to gamma radiation. As the Hulk, he possesses immense strength and becomes a formidable force against evildoers.

T'Challa, the king of Wakanda, possesses enhanced abilities and intelligence as a result of consuming the heart-shaped herb. With his Vibranium suit and advanced technology, he protects his nation and fights for justice.

Stephen Strange, a brilliant neurosurgeon, becomes a powerful sorcerer after a career-ending accident. As Doctor Strange, he protects the Earth from mystical threats and safeguards the fabric of reality.
